---
title: Herby Bacon-Wrapped Pork Roast with Dilly Cucumber Salad, Corn and Cheesy Biscuits
description: This is one special summer supper! Each bite of rich, roasted, bacon-wrapped pork goes perfectly with flaky and fluffy cheddar biscuits! P.S.: They also make a great sandwich for leftovers the next day.
